name: LIGHTHOUSE
description:
Youth and caution are incompatible.
The blood boils, the soul requires decisive action.

I want to prove to myself and everyone that you are better.
And most importantly, young people cannot do without a lighthouse.

You have not yet realized that you only need to fight with yourself, 
and you are looking for landmarks around, looking for someone to be like, 
looking for someone else, looking for your lighthouse.

But sometimes this lighthouse, brightly illuminating your road, 
is devoured by the Darkness.

The younger generation doesn't think about it.


:: visuals: @cryptohamster | sound-design: @bisdvrk
